**When Called:** Entity ID retrieved from cache

**Actions:**
1. Fetch full Entity object from DB using cached ID
2. Validate request version (skip stale requests)
3. Compare fingerprints to determine if entity changed
4. Route to appropriate fingerprint handler (same/different with/without lock)

